7a869-394a-4a4c-9275-9ada0737bdca" class="r-1d11viz" data-replo-collapsible="true" data-state="closed"><div data-rid="5498bd3d-f157-4732-8b06-b6d6512e7b95" aria-controls="replo-:Rvj2:" tabindex="0" role="button" class="r-8wfwrd"><div data-rid="7ef47e3c-8e39-41dd-a35d-af49d3f7cc2f" class="r-1jg8cjm alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>What makes TrueFit different from other protein powders?</p></span></div><div data-rid="4465420f-dfcc-407a-95ac-ebfb297e40b1" class="r-t2clos"><svg stroke="currentColor" fill="currentColor" stroke-width="0" viewBox="0 0 16 16" role="img" aria-label="Collapse/Expand" style="width:var(--rsw, 100%);height:auto;max-height:100%" class="r-mpvnh4" height="1em" width="1em" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M8 4a.5.5 0 0 1 .5.5v3h3a.5.5 0 0 1 0 1h-3v3a.5.5 0 0 1-1 0v-3h-3a.5.5 0 0 1 0-1h3v-3A.5.5 0 0 1 8 4"></path></svg></div></div><div hidden="" id="replo-:Rvj2:"><div data-rid="d480b3b1-8720-48f8-a9ef-c6ec10223a17" class="r-1li62xm"><div data-rid="a86897e5-b309-40bd-bd50-d0fb5cb42dc3" class="r-1c4aj2q alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0)">TrueFit is a whole foods meal replacement or protein supplement designed with your health in mind. A scoop of TrueFit contains not only 25g of protein, but a superfood blend of Non-GMO organic fruits and veggies and a digestive blend with probiotics, prebiotics, and 4g of fiber. TrueFit contains no GMOs, gluten, soy, artificial ingredients or preservatives. Plus, it tastes delicious!</span></p></span></div></div></div></div><div data-rid="b652df23-2390-43fe-8120-475eb80ee5ed" class="r-1xfzt31" data-replo-collapsible="true" data-state="closed"><div data-rid="4784a4dd-53e8-49a7-a705-1ccf19ca90ee" aria-controls="replo-:R1fj2:" tabindex="0" role="button" class="r-1dc266s"><div data-rid="04864c36-cd0e-4f07-8e84-bfe61175d126" class="r-o7p0rz alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p><span>Is TrueFit a good meal replacement?</span></p></span></div><div data-rid="5d45279a-68cf-4e60-b7ec-a451b4c4dd95" class="r-1c46ssd"><svg stroke="currentColor" fill="currentColor" stroke-width="0" viewBox="0 0 16 16" role="img" aria-label="Collapse/Expand" style="width:var(--rsw, 100%);height:auto;max-height:100%" class="r-i47okz" height="1em" width="1em" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M8 4a.5.5 0 0 1 .5.5v3h3a.5.5 0 0 1 0 1h-3v3a.5.5 0 0 1-1 0v-3h-3a.5.5 0 0 1 0-1h3v-3A.5.5 0 0 1 8 4"></path></svg></div></div><div hidden="" id="replo-:R1fj2:"><div data-rid="2ee7b699-2b67-4bc0-881e-81bbb26a90e6" class="r-gc9vtl"><div data-rid="133bfc73-e07f-4822-845f-12e47ac15dcd" class="r-1gctn49 alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>Yes — it contains protein, fiber, probiotics, and whole-food nutrients to create a balanced, satisfying meal in seconds.</p></span></div></div></div></div><div data-rid="70abd621-e6b2-409e-a3fc-4f2c5f53af15" class="r-12pwfc8" data-replo-collapsible="true" data-state="closed"><div data-rid="c5acb860-d679-457b-96c4-e3fed080edd0" aria-controls="replo-:R1vj2:" tabindex="0" role="button" class="r-1it0eme"><div data-rid="fe98f744-99f0-4719-bef1-84fb9db6e8f5" class="r-1ifmw01 alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>Should I use TrueFit if I'm on GLP-1 medications?</p></span></div><div data-rid="d396f999-22ad-4967-89be-f2a7c5c93b46" class="r-9mwtx9"><svg stroke="currentColor" fill="currentColor" stroke-width="0" viewBox="0 0 16 16" role="img" aria-label="Collapse/Expand" style="width:var(--rsw, 100%);height:auto;max-height:100%" class="r-6qfzor" height="1em" width="1em" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M8 4a.5.5 0 0 1 .5.5v3h3a.5.5 0 0 1 0 1h-3v3a.5.5 0 0 1-1 0v-3h-3a.5.5 0 0 1 0-1h3v-3A.5.5 0 0 1 8 4"></path></svg></div></div><div hidden="" id="replo-:R1vj2:"><div data-rid="39d7d4bf-15ca-4d44-b25c-f073e6de8ca0" class="r-2bwr0x"><div data-rid="e81f5e1d-65e7-4bdd-9899-f9d2d706e289" class="r-1hl721t alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0)">Absolutely. GLP-1 medications suppress appetite — TrueFit complements that effect by giving you a nutrient-dense, high-protein shake that keeps you satisfied for hours. Perfect for days when you don’t feel hungry enough for a full meal but still need quality nutrition.</span></p></span></div></div></div></div><div data-rid="97842adf-3aa2-4264-b0c2-84f996f68dae" class="r-fsgu1f" data-replo-collapsible="true" data-state="closed"><div data-rid="7eb5d553-7312-41ce-94f8-736e1b4476a8" aria-controls="replo-:R2fj2:" tabindex="0" role="button" class="r-f6bp7e"><div data-rid="c8fde09f-fd0f-4686-b264-30bbbd2e2038" class="r-tneje6 alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><h3>Can I use TrueFit even if I'm not on GLP-1 medications?</h3></span></div><div data-rid="685b1abd-5df6-4ebd-a450-810ff36226b5" class="r-1d3j1ti"><svg stroke="currentColor" fill="currentColor" stroke-width="0" viewBox="0 0 16 16" role="img" aria-label="Collapse/Expand" style="width:var(--rsw, 100%);height:auto;max-height:100%" class="r-11q37v3" height="1em" width="1em" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M8 4a.5.5 0 0 1 .5.5v3h3a.5.5 0 0 1 0 1h-3v3a.5.5 0 0 1-1 0v-3h-3a.5.5 0 0 1 0-1h3v-3A.5.5 0 0 1 8 4"></path></svg></div></div><div hidden="" id="replo-:R2fj2:"><div data-rid="ab84d01b-84fb-43b2-b785-cd2decc7867f" class="r-1m36k1s"><div data-rid="4ca9c8ea-7d6a-45f7-949c-e8e8d91b39a2" class="r-lq1v1o alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0)">Absolutely. TrueFit works as a natural appetite-supporting, muscle-preserving, clean protein shake for anyone trying to lose weight or improve nutrition.</span></p></span></div></div></div></div><div data-rid="d5372545-ea29-40f7-99ab-f9c60181efa6" class="r-1anf4o4" data-replo-collapsible="true" data-state="closed"><div data-rid="f78c07d8-1ea0-4708-9c92-874098ee9b28" aria-controls="replo-:R2vj2:" tabindex="0" role="button" class="r-1uddlly"><div data-rid="5ae67de9-0fdc-4c8b-90cd-62b1b7283155" class="r-1px5ny3 alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>When should I take TrueFit?</p></span></div><div data-rid="87becf68-4af5-4865-8b21-f7166ed766cd" class="r-126xwry"><svg stroke="currentColor" fill="currentColor" stroke-width="0" viewBox="0 0 16 16" role="img" aria-label="Collapse/Expand" style="width:var(--rsw, 100%);height:auto;max-height:100%" class="r-o9l69i" height="1em" width="1em" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M8 4a.5.5 0 0 1 .5.5v3h3a.5.5 0 0 1 0 1h-3v3a.5.5 0 0 1-1 0v-3h-3a.5.5 0 0 1 0-1h3v-3A.5.5 0 0 1 8 4"></path></svg></div></div><div hidden="" id="replo-:R2vj2:"><div data-rid="a7b5e3ec-883f-4ade-b63f-a9a356aff022" class="r-611nmt"><div data-rid="a5535e9a-6490-4d5b-84fc-3c156a5f3177" class="r-13oevvx alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>TrueFit is designed to fit seamlessly into any weight-loss routine — with or without GLP-1 medications. You can take it any time you need a filling, nutrient-dense option, but most customers prefer it:</p><p><br>Morning: as a balanced, high-protein breakfast that sets the tone for the day<br><br>Midday: as an easy, satisfying lunch replacement<br><br>Post-Workout: to support lean muscle and recovery<br><br>On low-appetite days: when GLP-1 medications make full meals difficult<br><br>Evenings: as a clean, sweet-tooth-satisfying shake without derailing goals</p></span></div></div></div></div><div data-rid="7a7f1d2d-de64-4e8c-8af0-a67adfab179b" class="r-ht7fgd" data-replo-collapsible="true" data-state="closed"><div data-rid="54aafb95-6124-42f1-8b94-08e27d7c6b86" aria-controls="replo-:R3fj2:" tabindex="0" role="button" class="r-ptqq9r"><div data-rid="b7dd0586-c464-476a-a012-a48cc94acb60" class="r-p3bu4d alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p><span>Will TrueFit help preserve muscle while losing weight?</span></p></span></div><div data-rid="60768c5a-53fd-4fc3-8e92-f307ddf96fce" class="r-1y9idqc"><svg stroke="currentColor" fill="currentColor" stroke-width="0" viewBox="0 0 16 16" role="img" aria-label="Collapse/Expand" style="width:var(--rsw, 100%);height:auto;max-height:100%" class="r-w1s46s" height="1em" width="1em" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M8 4a.5.5 0 0 1 .5.5v3h3a.5.5 0 0 1 0 1h-3v3a.5.5 0 0 1-1 0v-3h-3a.5.5 0 0 1 0-1h3v-3A.5.5 0 0 1 8 4"></path></svg></div></div><div hidden="" id="replo-:R3fj2:"><div data-rid="a0d35919-dfbf-4a48-9d70-e77fc5e12466" class="r-kfsy0d"><div data-rid="ab518016-f3dd-4302-ade4-79f2d8fac311" class="r-q0plho alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>Yes. The 25g grass-fed whey protein helps prevent muscle loss and supports a healthy metabolism during calorie reduction.</p></span></div></div></div></div><div data-rid="8b781f8b-c952-49cf-a2a7-c86e752094db" class="r-1jzokq" data-replo-collapsible="true" data-state="closed"><div data-rid="d78b5ecf-6930-4369-9255-b4c524d2f9d3" aria-controls="replo-:R3vj2:" tabindex="0" role="button" class="r-8zj8g5"><div data-rid="0ce42cf0-b7bf-459f-8215-98d53a8b1462" class="r-kgyjk alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><h3>Is TrueFit low in sugar?</h3></span></div><div data-rid="09a5db10-e65d-420a-9c53-30c94d1c0cae" class="r-pvmxx"><svg stroke="currentColor" fill="currentColor" stroke-width="0" viewBox="0 0 16 16" role="img" aria-label="Collapse/Expand" style="width:var(--rsw, 100%);height:auto;max-height:100%" class="r-8xj103" height="1em" width="1em" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M8 4a.5.5 0 0 1 .5.5v3h3a.5.5 0 0 1 0 1h-3v3a.5.5 0 0 1-1 0v-3h-3a.5.5 0 0 1 0-1h3v-3A.5.5 0 0 1 8 4"></path></svg></div></div><div hidden="" id="replo-:R3vj2:"><div data-rid="6be4be97-e097-4a8c-a119-b743b0ae9132" class="r-reabfy"><div data-rid="17bfd303-2a9f-442f-8fec-97c009f4aff8" class="r-1grtnte alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0)">Yes — just 3g of sugar per serving, naturally flavored.</span></p></span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><style>@import url(https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@100;200;300;400;500;600;700;800;900;950&family=Inter:wght@100;200;300;400;500;600;700;800;900;950)</style></div>
